name: Ant-eater
description:
This is from a set of drawings and watercolors, based on proper animal behavior and a tale like surrounding. This is a print on smooth rag 210 g/m 100% cotton paper from Canson, a Giclee Print
28 x 38cm 
there are more of these so hopefully i will be rotating them.

-All prints are signed on the back and come in a strong pvc tube to ensure a safe journey out of chile, i wrap the print with a thin acid free paper, every one is packaged with love and care.

name: Costate Cockle
description:
this print is from a series of smaller paintings that im making with watercolor, pen, graphite, oil, enamel, acrilic and silver leaf, this will be a Lambda print on photographic paper, i enhanced the diamond in this print with a Silver leaf, just like the original, 
soon there will be more of this series.
the size of this one is 56 x 63cm

name: Tzadkiel
description:
Tzadkiel is the second archangel of a series of 7 angels i painted the last couple of years, this is a print on smooth rag 210 g/m 100% cotton paper from Canson Giclee Print, the size is 36 x 57cm
Tzadkiel is Angel of Abundance, triumph, long journeys, expancion, and more. the original painting is 210 x 150cm and is showing in Santiago Chile for know but id like them to keep on moving and travel all over.

-All prints are signed on the back and come in a strong pvc tube to ensure a safe journey out of chille, i wrap the print with a thin acid free paper, every one is packaged with love and care.
